Normal class => NC

Abstract class => AC

Interface class => IC

to do inheritance in java, we use extends and implements keywords

**when to use extends keywords and implements keywords,

		super/parent/base class				keyword				sub/child/derived class
	
				NC 							extends		 				NC
				AC							extends						NC
				IC						   implements					NC
 				NC							extends						AC
 				AC							extends                     AC
 				IC						   implements					AC
 		
			 	NC						   Not possible*				IC
			 	AC						   Not possible*				IC
			 	
			 	IC 							extends						IC                                              